{"tid":2070903,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU粉絲為撐偶像購入股票　十年股價翻漲35倍","createTime":"2020-06-19T12:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T06:06:55.000Z","uid":34643,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d14b5cb16135b8b950036ce96054bc9b8f744859","tid":2070903,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:22:14.000Z","msg":"好多人覺得追星係浪費金錢時間嘅事，但原來都有勵志例子﹗韓國藝人IU入行以來都受到粉絲愛戴，韓媒報導有一位粉絲十年前為支持偶像，以3萬元韓元（約$191港元）購入公司股票，隨住IU歌影視三棲發展愈來愈紅，股價隨之急劇上漲﹗十年後今日股票價值近104萬2000韓元（約$6585港元），升值近35倍﹗<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200617/349959386938085376.jpeg/CnpP4c3tWJbxTfo0HualrNvNKPllelg-RQ9irkUPYq4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200617%2F349959386938085376.jpeg%2FCnpP4c3tWJbxTfo0HualrNvNKPllelg-RQ9irkUPYq4&h=53cc4697&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25dd86356f919277d1125e32233e26035cc49bc9","tid":2070903,"uid":49004,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:24:25.000Z","msg":"信iu得永生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8997176ab85f831e14ae3cefad180080946375a","tid":2070903,"uid":76632,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:26:26.000Z","msg":"IU早期嘅絕版週邊、絕版黑膠唱片都升值萬倍，千金難求<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"f8947d7c4015fdd500d723379bf8eacaa24bb03d","tid":2070903,"uid":70274,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"25dd86356f919277d1125e32233e26035cc49bc9","tid":2070903,"uid":49004,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:24:25.000Z","msg":"信iu得永生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zL5emYp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzL5emYp.jpg&h=b1606745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢有矛比人metoo過"},{"pid":"fd774e5d1529d39df4c72c6d140063e1673